{
  "id": "RAW_7a89bc",
  "title": "从工具到 Agent：我们正失去「停止权」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/CfUfPb2MQ_Y3epA0ZQr9fg",
  "date": "2025-03-27 08:07:40",
  "author": "金色传说大聪明",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(10px);padding:32px 16px;text-wrap:wrap;color:rgb(21 18 47 / 80%);background-attachment:fixed;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;margin-block-end:0.75em;text-indent:0em;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;background-image:linear-gradient(62deg, rgb(142 197 252 / 20%) 0%, hsl(271deg 90% 88% / 20%) 100%);text-align:left;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <h2 style=\"border-radius:2px 12px;padding:8px 12px;margin:auto;font-weight:600;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);letter-spacing:1px;width:fit-content;font-size:24px;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\">之前参加了一场 OpenAI 的活动，主题是管理「自主 AI 系统」（Agentic Systems）。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">那时聊了很多有关 Agent 的问题，恰是当下各种 Agent 项目正需面对的。</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;line-height: 120%;\"><span leaf=\"\">讨论多是基于论文《P</span><span leaf=\"\">ractices for Governing Agentic AI Systems》，地址是：https://openai.com/research/practices-for-governing-agentic-ai-systems</span></span></p>\n    <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;visibility: visible;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"373\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"700\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" data-ratio=\"0.6824074074074075\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0db3787d-7fa2-4a1a-edba-94cfd99db300/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 645px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0db3787d-7fa2-4a1a-edba-94cfd99db300/public\"></span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\">明确一下：</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 会面对这些挑战，并非是其水平不行，而是更早的开始探索边界。</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;text-align: right;\"><span style=\"\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\">&nbsp;-- 大家都将会遇到</span></span></strong></span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);margin: 20px 0px;\">\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 的定义，目前已经严重泛化了：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">两个人在讨论「Agent」，他们讨论的可能都不是同一种东西</span>。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">按当前的语境，我们会把&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT 就是看成一种 AI 应用，它能理解你的问题并给出回答。而会把 GPTs 这种订制后的、能调用外部功能的、能够自己处理复杂任务的产品，叫做 Agent。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Agent 和 AI 应用（如ChatGPT）之间的区别和联系主要体现在“代理性”（agenticness）</span>。如果一个AI系统，能够在没有直接人类监督的情况下运作，其自主性越高，我们称之为代理性越强。</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个连续体，不是非黑即白的判断，而是根据它在特定环境中的表现来评估其代理性的程度。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这种定义下，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">正统 Agent 不仅能回答问题，还能自己决定做什么，它能够通过生成文本来“思考”</span>，然后做出一些操作，甚至能创造出更多的 AI 帮手来帮帮忙，就比如下面这个图。（</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">仔细看这个 Twitter 图，时间是 2 年前</span></strong></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">）</span></span></p>\n    <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"667\" data-backw=\"520\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" data-ratio=\"1.2824074074074074\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7f188edd-29ac-420c-16a0-dbe540c03400/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7f188edd-29ac-420c-16a0-dbe540c03400/public\">\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">（再补一张2年前， 时任 OpenAI Dev Rel 的 Logan 的发言）</span></span></p>\n    <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n     <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100007973\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d04f13e-28ef-4890-0b2b-36c88538fe00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d04f13e-28ef-4890-0b2b-36c88538fe00/public\">\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">但我们发现，尽管 Agent 看起来很美好，但在实际落地的场景中，也是困难重重，风险多多，出现了问题，责任划分也很麻烦。比如这里：如果我希望让某个 Agent 帮我微信收款，但它给别人展示的是付款码，那么这里谁背锅？</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些问题，也将会是 o1 在真正行业落地时，所要面对的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n    <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);margin: 20px 0px;\">\n   </section>\n   <h2 style=\"border-radius:2px 12px;padding:8px 12px;margin:auto;font-weight:600;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);letter-spacing:1px;width:fit-content;font-size:24px;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">落地难点</span></h2>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-block-end: 12px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\">由于会上的 PPT 不便分享，我便在自己吸收后，重新制作了一份 PPT，安心食用</span></span></p>\n    <p><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">01</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">执行效果评估</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5206c3b5-dff1-4926-31e3-ab5fd76d7700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-backw=\"520\" data-backh=\"293\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5206c3b5-dff1-4926-31e3-ab5fd76d7700/public\"></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">在商业环境中，确保任何工具的可靠性是基本要求。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，AI Agent 的复杂性在于其工作场景和任务的不确定性。例如，一个在模拟环境中表现优异的自动驾驶车辆，可能因现实世界中不可预测的变量（如天气变化和道路条件）而表现不稳定。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们尚缺乏有效的方法，来准确评估 AI Agent 在实际环境中的性能。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">02</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">危险行为界定</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"293\" data-backw=\"520\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e20f47bd-1abf-44ea-9e15-06fc87d18c00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e20f47bd-1abf-44ea-9e15-06fc87d18c00/public\"></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI Agent 在执行高风险操作之前需要获得用户的明确批准。例如，在金融领域，AI 执行大额转账前必须得到用户同意。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">但需要注意，频繁的审批请求可能导致用户出现审批疲劳，从而可能无视风险盲目批准操作，这既削弱了批准机制的效果，也可能增加操作风险。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">03</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">默认行为确定</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c277c4a9-8b77-4f2e-efa3-c960b3999000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-backw=\"520\" data-backh=\"293\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c277c4a9-8b77-4f2e-efa3-c960b3999000/public\"></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">当 AI Agent 遇到执行错误或不确定的情形时，是要有一个默认行为的。例如，如果一个客服机器人在不确定用户需求时，其默认行为是请求更多信息以避免错误操作。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，频繁的请求可能会影响用户体验，因此在保障系统安全性与保持用户体验之间需要找到平衡。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">04</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">推理透明展示</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/59275ecd-8876-41b1-eee5-1e685b4c6a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-backw=\"520\" data-backh=\"293\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/59275ecd-8876-41b1-eee5-1e685b4c6a00/public\"></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了保证 AI Agent 决策的透明性，系统需要向用户清晰展示其推理过程。举例来说，一个健康咨询机器人应详细解释其提出特定医疗建议的逻辑。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果推理过程太复杂，普通用户可能难以理解，这就需要在确保透明性和易理解性之间找到平衡。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">05</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 行为监控</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/db801266-d86d-4dce-063a-dfcf6123af00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-backw=\"520\" data-backh=\"293\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/db801266-d86d-4dce-063a-dfcf6123af00/public\"></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">假设一个 AI 系统用于监控仓库库存，如果监控系统误报，误认为某项商品缺货，进而不断的进货，那么可能导致库存的严重积压，并造成极大损失。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是，我们思考：是否需要另一个 Agent 来监控这个 Agent？成本账怎么算？</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">06</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 作恶追责</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ec0a3cd0-64fc-4d91-71b4-73dd6e936200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-backw=\"520\" data-backh=\"293\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ec0a3cd0-64fc-4d91-71b4-73dd6e936200/public\"></span>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">考虑一个匿名发布内容的 AI Agent，如果其发布了违规内容，要追踪到具体负责的人或机构可能极其困难。这种情况下，建立一个能够确保责任可追溯的系统尤为关键，同时还需要平衡隐私保护和责任追究的需求。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding-bottom: 0.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <section style=\"height: 72px;\">\n     <section style=\"border-radius:4px 12px;margin:8px 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;width:72px;font-size:16px;height:48px;\">\n      <section style=\"backdrop-filter:blur(12px);margin:-8px -8px;font-weight:bold;font-size:32px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);line-height:48px;border-radius:4px 12px;background:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);width:72px;border-width:1px;border-style:solid;height:48px;text-align:center;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">07</span>\n      </section>\n     </section><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 28px;opacity: 0.8;line-height: 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\">严重事故叫停</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <em><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb6fada8-9757-4c8a-c6cf-43effac4fb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-radius: 12px;margin: 12px auto;width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"520\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"260\" data-backw=\"520\" data-backh=\"293\" data-imgfileid=\"100003767\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bb6fada8-9757-4c8a-c6cf-43effac4fb00/public\"></span></em>\n     <p style=\"margin-block-end: 0.5em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><span leaf=\"\">想象一个用于自动化工厂管理的 AI Agent，在系统检测到严重故障需要立即停机时，不仅需要停止主控系统，还要同步关闭所有从属设备和流程。如何设计一个能够迅速且全面响应的紧急停止机制，以防止故障扩散或造成更大损失，是一项技术和策略上的复杂挑战。</span></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);margin: 20px 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 1em auto;\">\n    <h2 style=\"border-radius:2px 12px;padding:8px 12px;margin:auto;font-weight:600;background:linear-gradient(90deg, #9c69f2, #70b0f9);letter-spacing:1px;width:fit-content;font-size:24px;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后</span></h2>\n    <section style=\"border-radius:16px;padding:16px 12px;box-shadow:#4e73ff22 0px 4px 30px;backdrop-filter:blur(5px);border-width:1px;border-color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);border-style:solid;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">个人来说，希望大家来思考这个问题</span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\">《</span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247489796&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=2d2a1c814e4703d3a3ab6b83c76ea634&amp;chksm=c2bcd402f5cb5d1491c4fd69f50d64c8a2738f4981635c213f378a3e3cfac8a59ed68cd80a05&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"对于 AI &amp; AGI，我有 3 个问题\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">对于 AI &amp; AGI，我有 3 个问题</a></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">》</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "探讨了自主 AI 系统 (Agent) 在落地应用中面临的挑战，以及由此带来的“失去停止权”的风险。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "探讨了自主 AI 系统 (Agent) 在落地应用中面临的挑战，以及由此带来的“失去停止权”的风险。",
  "summary": "本文深入探讨了当前 Agent (自主 AI 系统) 在实际应用中面临的诸多挑战与风险，以及由此带来的“失去停止权”的风险。文章首先阐述了 Agent 的定义及其与传统 AI 应用的区别，强调了 Agent 的自主性。随后，文章着重分析了 Agent 在落地过程中遇到的七大难点，涉及执行效果评估、风险控制、责任追溯等方面。每个难点都结合实际案例进行了深入剖析，并提出了相应的解决思路。文章旨在提醒开发者和使用者在享受 Agent 带来的便利的同时，也要充分认识到其潜在的风险，并采取有效的措施加以规避。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Agent 落地应用面临执行效果评估的挑战",
      "explanation": "由于 Agent 工作场景和任务的不确定性，难以准确评估其在实际环境中的性能，需要更有效的评估方法。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Agent 的危险行为界定需要用户明确批准，但可能导致“失去停止权”的风险",
      "explanation": "频繁的审批请求可能导致用户审批疲劳，从而可能无视风险盲目批准操作，需要在安全性和便捷性之间找到平衡。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Agent 作恶后的追责面临挑战",
      "explanation": "匿名 Agent 发布违规内容时，追踪责任人或机构困难，需建立可追溯系统，同时平衡隐私保护和责任追究。"
    },
    {
      "point": "是否需要另一个 Agent 来监控 Agent？",
      "explanation": "监控 Agent 的成本和有效性需要仔细衡量。"
    }
